{"tid":1323770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Charles Mok 莫乃光 提出左樣要注意既野","createTime":"2019-07-16T10:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T11:12:17.000Z","uid":273289,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"12fc37da440e181c610b428af057499c8b5c0d2b","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"Charles Mok 莫乃光<br />\n&middot; <br />\n【戒嚴？斷網？】<br />\n今日有報導指政府正研究分區戒嚴，事關重大，因為特首可引用法例權力對通訊進行管制，甚至最嚴重的&ldquo;斷網&rdquo;。這種做法可能嚴重破壞香港資訊自由的形象，影響互聯網和電訊業運作牽連甚大，&rdquo;斷網&ldquo;一旦發生香港更可能變成非洲獨裁國家的水平。任何影響通訊和電訊的措施必須十分謹慎考量，絕對不能戒嚴和斷網！<br />\n<br />\n相關法例：<br />\n第241章 《緊急情況規例條例》 ─ 第2條 訂立規例的權力<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/&hellip;/cap241!zh-Hant-HK@2018-12&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fcap241%21zh-Hant-HK%402018-12%E2%80%A6&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=68601296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/&hellip;/cap241!zh-Hant-HK@2018-12&hellip;</a><br />\n(1) 在行政長官會同行政會議認為屬 緊急情況或危害公安的情況時 ，行政長官會同行政會議 可訂立任何他認為合乎公眾利益的規例 。<br />\n(2)在不損害第(1)款條文的一般性的原則下，該等規例可就下列事項作出規定<br />\n(a)對刊物、文字、地圖、圖則、照片、 通訊及通訊方法的檢查、管制及壓制 ；<br />\n<br />\n第106章《電訊條例》第13條 在緊急情況下由政府接管電訊電台<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap106!zh-Hant-HK&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap106%21zh-Hant-HK%E2%80%A6&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=a3fe819b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap106!zh-Hant-HK&hellip;</a><br />\n若行政長官認為已發生緊急情況，可簽署手令接管或使用電訊電台，或對其加以控制，手令有效期不多於一週，但可以連續每週發出。條例沒有列明何謂「緊急情況」。<br />\n<br />\n如果佢BLOCK 網路同街燈<br />\n問題1咁警察係唔係都只有無線電?<br />\n問題2 示威通訊問題"},{"pid":"d9c4a470863fc3171556a078e8a9df9cd59da51b","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:00:05.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"2d63a34c39d86cef2a532f32741e2bf29b489468","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"6ba7ec38f6c182bf24e1d0040ca4fff3f740c954","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:00:27.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"34fae98acb25867af2936c3c02837fe4a9049676","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:00:37.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"e5766d9870c72c1626140d4e66ade61a25e19fc3","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:00:47.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"25fbe52811bf023aaf392fcfa099b8f20336d1a5","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:00:58.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"32fbd2b8d92bb071aa6d7e03fa6512325dd2e0ed","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:01:08.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"df28cfe2de954f96ea6b63c64ed32912834eb7b9","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:01:18.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"953d1309b6af168df09c7e42a7e4f226e90b9f29","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:01:28.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"1903673d22334b57d14c9d94a54a75cea89e508c","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:01:38.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"7199b3164429585f2e0fdae589ba727e2599d14c","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:01:48.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"04874565e222efd0e90e2b5ab4aea1e0976c07a0","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:02:15.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"3bd6b5b23ddc9904934729476c510c91b9d10abc","tid":1323770,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pi